What is the main problem described in this issue?

Issue: Make table ddl task work with catalog

Table related ddl task should respect catalog. Such as these syntax: {code:java} create table cat.db.tbl(id int); alter table cat.db.tbl set .. {code}

What is the main problem described in this issue?

Issue: Invalid index should return null for get_json_object

{{get_json_object}} index is numeric, but current implement will return the entire array string for invalid index like {*}$[1 ]{*}. {code:sql} hive> select get_json_object('[1,2,3]', "$[1 ]"); [1,2,3] {code}

